  { type: 'text', content: "Let Simbali Wild Safaris build Samburu into a private Kenya journey with the right season, lodge style, and guiding pace. <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"text-olive underline font-semibold\">Contact us</a> and we will shape the route around the safari you actually want to feel." },
